'''Luigi Ferraris''' (Legnano, 1962) is an Italian executive, Chief Executive Officer of [[Terna Group|Terna S.p.A.]] since April 2017.<ref>[https://www.terna.it/en-gb/azienda/chisiamo/strutturaorganizzativa/luigiferraris-amministratoredelegato.aspx Luigi Ferraris has been Chief Executive Officer of Terna ]</ref> CEO of Enersis <ref>[https://www.seas.sk/article/enel-ferraris-is-new-head-of-latam-area-de-paoli-is-new-cfo/129 ENEL: FERRARIS IS NEW HEAD OF LATAM AREA, DE PAOLI IS NEW CFO]</ref> from 2014 to 2015, ex - Chairman of [[Enel Green Power]],  CFO of [[Enel Group]] and current Chief Financial Officer of [[Poste Italiane |Poste Italiane Group]].<ref>[https://www.crunchbase.com/person/luigi-ferraris#/ Luigi Ferraris Chief Financial Officer of Poste Italiane Group]</ref> Luigi Ferraris was also Chairman of Enel Green Power S.p.A.<ref>[http://mcr.doingbusiness.ro/news/enel-green-power-board-of-directors-approves-results-for-2012/1667 Enel Green Power: Board of directors approves results for 2012]</ref> as well as Operating Chairman of Enel Factor S.p.A. In 2015 Luigi Ferraris was appointed Chief Financial Officer of Poste Italiane Group, in charge of managing its privatization process, one of the largest ever undertaken in Italy.<ref>[http://www.italy24.ilsole24ore.com/art/markets/2015-01-30/enel-buy-back-134326.php?uuid=AB3NWdmC Poste renews its executive team to get ready for privatization]</ref>  He has had also the responsibility of implementing the Group’s Risk and Management Control functions, while starting a valorisation and optimization plan for Group’s Real Estate properties. Luigi Ferraris worked also as non executive Board Member of [[Banca del Mezzogiorno – MedioCredito Centrale|Banca del Mezzogiorno – Mediocredito Centrale]], PSC S.p.A Group. He was Board Member of [[Erg S.p.A.]]<ref>[http://www.erg.eu/en/corporate-governance/board-of-directors Luigi Ferraris ex Board Member of Erg S.p.A. ]</ref> a company listed in the Italian stock exchange. He had a teaching role or “Corporate Strategy” at LUISS University.<ref>[http://businessschool.luiss.it/faculty-research/adjunct-faculty/ferraris-luigi/ Luigi Ferraris professor at the Economics Department at the “Luiss Guido Carli” University]</ref>

